Inclusion Criteria:

1. Both male and female;
2. Age from 18 to 65 years;
3. Documented history of CU for at least 6 weeks prior to entry in the study;
4. Meet EAACI/GA2LEN/EDF/WAO 2017 guidelines, i.e. spontaneous appearance of wheals, angioedema or both for \> 6 weeks due to known or unknown cause

